The Viewglob CVS repository is accessible on the web from here:

    (this is obsolete - use the subversion checkout below instead)
    http://sourceforge.net/cvs/?group_id=116249

For anonymous subversion checkout:

    (this is also obsolete - see below)
    svn checkout https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/viewglob/trunk/viewglob

Even better:

    git clone git://github.com/sjbach/viewglob.git

Tab spacing for *.[ch] files is 4.  Optimized for an 80 column width.

